The Commission seeks comment on this proposal. 




Filings to recover stranded costs in transmission rates during the transition period will be permitted regardless
of whether the service is voluntarily provided (under section 205 of the FPA pursuant to an open-access tariff, a tariff
of general applicability or an individual contract) or mandated under section 211 of the FPA. However, the Commission
