<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY:

 The Department of Energy proposes to amend the Department of Energy Acquisition Regulation (DEAR) to establish DOE
policies and procedures for establishing a program to achieve a ten percent goal for awards of prime contracts and
subcontracts for specific types of universities and of small disadvantaged concerns, including women-owned businesses,
in the implementation of section 3021 of the Energy Policy Act of 1992.

 
