evaluation is not required because the rule, if adopted, would have no mandatory effects. Instead, the proposal would
only codify a longstanding agency interpretation. Therefore, this rulemaking would not have any cost impacts.


2. Regulatory Flexibility Act


In accordance with the Regulatory Flexibility Act, NHTSA has evaluated the effects of this action on small entities.
Based upon this evaluation, I certify that the proposed amendment would not have a significant economic impact on
