petitioned taxa, especially any threat associated with a population decline. Many of the species covered by this
petition may be sensitive to ecological perturbations resulting from the impacts of human activities. However,
information was not presented to show correlations between the species' ecological sensitivity and any declines
in population numbers. The taxonomic distinctiveness or validity of many of the species has not been determined.


